Peugeot Elis Rechargeable Wine Opener Gift Set
List.Description:
Peugeot began in the 19th century with manufacturing of kitchen items such as pepper and coffee grinders. More than 160 years later, it is still recognized as a premiere French brand. The Peugeot Stainless-Steel Elis Rechargeable Wine Corkscrew fits in all bottle necks and allows quick and effortless bottle uncorking – even synthetic corks. Its beautiful stainless-steel finish looks elegant in the kitchen or entertaining at party. This set also includes the Peugeot Jero Foil Cutter, which has four blade wheels and will cleanly cut the bottle foil regardless of the neck diameter, with just a quarter of a turn. Additionally, the Peugeot Arros drip-free pouring spouts make pouring into a glass or decanter simple and eliminates mess. Charging accessories also included. Gift Box included for storing all set items when not in-use.


Includes:
  • Stainless-Steel Rechargeable Wine Opener
  • Foil Cutter
  • 2 Pouring Spouts
  • Charging Cord
  • Gift Box
